Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.84,0:00:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What a nice wind...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.17,0:00:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.89,0:00:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it... Nice days like this\Nmake you wish you didn't have to work...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.10,0:00:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, what are you saying,\Ndeputy captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.94,0:00:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're like that who's gonna\Nset an example here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.69,0:00:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Gibbs, how long it's been\Nsince you came to this ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.20,0:00:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.37,0:00:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,About 8 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.79,0:00:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.33,0:00:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess this lifestyle was perfect for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.04,0:00:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems so.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.42,0:00:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,For me, it's been 3 years\Nsince I became deputy captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.55,0:00:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just call it captain\Nat this point?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.43,0:00:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's "deputy" for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.47,0:00:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't just simply drop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.61,0:01:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Capella, how's things?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.78,0:01:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.69,0:01:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The clouds are calm too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.65,0:01:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we have a tailwind,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.82,0:01:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,we might arrive to Quon town\Nin 3 days if it continues like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.87,0:01:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm leaving it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.66,0:01:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll finally be able to refuel!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.92,0:01:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,These days have been pretty rough\Nfor the ship after all,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.21,0:01:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,she's run-down.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.38,0:01:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta fix her up everywhere, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.97,0:01:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Quon is a big town,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.01,0:01:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,so take the chance to relax\Nas much as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.14,0:01:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.85,0:01:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,My shoulders have been so stiff lately...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.35,0:01:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll find a good massage shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.60,0:01:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Crocco-san do you know any?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.56,0:01:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha? How would I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.98,0:01:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe what I've been\Nlistening you say!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.86,0:01:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-Huh?\N-Since the latest departure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.36,0:01:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,we haven't captured almost any dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.53,0:01:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We did catch a few though?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.37,0:01:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We're a large crew here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.95,0:02:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,With just that we're so deep in the red\Nit's almost purple!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.45,0:02:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Refueling and reparations
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.96,0:02:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,are not cheap in the slightest, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.75,0:02:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand what I mean, right,\Ndeputy captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.80,0:02:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.34,0:02:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.59,0:02:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oof...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.97,0:02:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.85,0:02:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.14,0:02:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we have to peel all these today?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.39,0:02:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,These are sprouting already!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.86,0:02:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta take them all out, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.15,0:02:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to maintain a draking vessel,\Nwe need a huge amount of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.99,0:02:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragons are sold for a large sum,\Nso as long as we capture them\Nwe can cover the costs...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.74,0:02:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But when we don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.91,0:02:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We are the ones who have to starve...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.34,0:02:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.56,0:03:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,♪〜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.26,0:04:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,〜♪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.15,0:04:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... so tired of potatoes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.32,0:04:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And food's about the only thing\Nto look forward too...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.53,0:04:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I do wish I could prepare you\Nsomething else, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.83,0:04:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't allow it. The problem is that\Nyou always are wasting money.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.71,0:04:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But we do have dragons that we captured!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.37,0:04:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are for sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.25,0:04:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No one will notice if we take a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.92,0:04:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay, shall I deduct it\Nfrom your salary then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.38,0:04:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.26,0:05:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll arrive to a big town soon, won't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.05,0:05:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We just need to be a little patient!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.18,0:05:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.22,0:05:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sick of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.06,0:05:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Meat... let me eat dragon meat...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.39,0:05:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.56,0:05:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, eat some more!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.32,0:05:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.03,0:05:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna sleep the next 3 days off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.56,0:05:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do your work!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.53,0:05:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.62,0:05:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.04,0:05:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.46,0:05:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, nothing we can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.92,0:05:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,When we finish the delivery,\Nwe'll have some time off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.42,0:05:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I can get as many hangovers\Nas I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.51,0:05:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to sleep in a big bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.63,0:05:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.63,0:05:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No more sweaty beds for a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.93,0:05:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And... Right, Jiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.39,0:05:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're looking forward to it too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.60,0:05:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't play dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.86,0:05:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're to become a full-fledged\Nman of the crew...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.57,0:06:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to know what a woman is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.32,0:06:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.45,0:06:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you talk about that when\Nthere's no girls around...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.50,0:06:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-Jiro-san!\N-Stop already!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.33,0:06:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even need to say that\Nyou're paying yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.71,0:06:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.63,0:06:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid, stupid... stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.96,0:06:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Before we arrive to the town...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.76,0:06:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be great if we managed\Nto catch another one...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.22,0:06:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.93,0:06:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.43,0:06:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.68,0:06:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.89,0:06:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, that flag signal...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.39,0:06:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,An SOS!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.44,0:06:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... guys, do you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.11,0:06:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Vadakin?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to interrupt while you're eating\Nbut it's an emergency, look behind the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.04,0:06:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.75,0:06:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring the ship closer immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.00,0:06:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Of all things...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.34,0:07:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll approach it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.52,0:07:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an ocean cargo ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.81,0:07:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Going down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.99,0:07:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it's a shipwreck...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.45,0:07:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If it is, I hope they're alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.12,0:07:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.17,0:07:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like a pretty old ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.42,0:07:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't feel like there's anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.21,0:07:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we were too late...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.01,0:07:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! Then let's split up\Nand investigate!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.76,0:07:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.01,0:07:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, Vannie and me will go inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.39,0:07:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm raising them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.97,0:07:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.47,0:07:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'll go down to check.\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.73,0:07:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Faye and Soraya go check the crew room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.64,0:07:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yes ma'am!\N-Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.06,0:08:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ehhh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.57,0:08:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, Soraya, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.87,0:08:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,As empty as an abandoned shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.87,0:08:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's look all the way to the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.58,0:08:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.25,0:08:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.13,0:08:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I even said I wouldn't work anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.30,0:08:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.43,0:08:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.35,0:08:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If there are no bodies,\Ndoes that mean someone rescued them already?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.57,0:08:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.90,0:08:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of old books!\NHow nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.32,0:08:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Maybe we can sell them in the town!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.53,0:08:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, we're not thieves!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.82,0:08:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just borrow this poetry anthology.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.95,0:08:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn this ship, it was a false alarm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.09,0:08:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.71,0:09:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oww, that hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.79,0:09:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Soraya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.50,0:09:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.05,0:09:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems the floor was rotten!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.73,0:09:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How was over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.27,0:09:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.31,0:09:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I see a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.85,0:09:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.48,0:09:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, let's take down that flag\Nand go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.44,0:09:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If they got rescued they could have\Ntaken it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.65,0:09:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It just makes it confusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.49,0:09:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Right... it never rains but it pours...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.08,0:09:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,An airship?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.33,0:09:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.96,0:09:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Gibbs! Pull us up, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.50,0:09:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.67,0:09:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A ship is approaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.59,0:09:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! I'll lower the hooks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.97,0:09:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something wrong with that ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.64,0:09:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a bad feeling about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.64,0:09:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull them up quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.49,0:10:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,They're chasing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.20,0:10:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That outline...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.37,0:10:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Jiro-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.87,0:10:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll watch from above!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Rise at full speed, 10 to starboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.75,0:10:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.71,0:10:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So the rescue ship was just a bait...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.29,0:10:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.01,0:10:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They're faster than us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.68,0:10:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Vanabelle's bad feeling was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.77,0:10:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.31,0:10:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They're air pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.19,0:10:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, we're so lucky a draking vessel\Nfell for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.41,0:10:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They probably have dragon oil onboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.37,0:11:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice steering they've got there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.91,0:11:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But I won't let you escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.67,0:11:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They're catching up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.88,0:11:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to use more fuel\Nfor mere pirates, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.58,0:11:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same as always...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.05,0:11:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.86,0:11:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Their helmsman is very good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.92,0:11:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh! Our run-down ship is getting\Neven more run-down...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.17,0:11:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.63,0:11:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not the time to say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.39,0:12:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita! Crouch down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.82,0:12:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh... why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.45,0:12:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! Don't stand there dumbfounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.82,0:12:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.74,0:12:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... your eyelid...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.41,0:12:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine. It's just a scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.79,0:12:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.51,0:12:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare they...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.97,0:12:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't even care for women\Nand children?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.89,0:12:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, go inside! Quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.90,0:12:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.24,0:13:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,When I shoot one, ten come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.32,0:13:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't fight a machine gun with\Nsingle shot guns!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.08,0:13:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Bridge! We're at a disadvantage\Nin this position.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.87,0:13:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,At least raise the ship over them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.87,0:13:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.42,0:13:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta do it, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.38,0:13:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro here! I arrived to the lookout.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.71,0:13:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They plan to board our ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.80,0:13:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Tsk...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.51,0:13:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A kite?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.47,0:13:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They intend to board us from\Nthe lookout.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.47,0:13:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.56,0:13:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro! Get out of there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.18,0:13:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Vanabelle, cover me when I go out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.69,0:13:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.40,0:13:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna board them instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.03,0:13:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.11,0:13:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.53,0:13:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.61,0:13:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.11,0:13:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.46,0:13:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh... Mika?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.59,0:14:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.98,0:14:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This thing isn't made to aim for\Nsmall targets...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.94,0:14:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Niko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.36,0:14:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say about small targets?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.74,0:14:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What are you waiting for?\NBoard them already!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.62,0:14:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys! Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.92,0:14:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah? What's he...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.05,0:14:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!! Wait, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.07,0:15:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha- He's acting on his own again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.53,0:15:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.16,0:15:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah- Eh, wha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.62,0:15:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, no way, no waaaay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.17,0:15:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.13,0:15:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He boarded us alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.47,0:15:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he sane?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.43,0:15:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't flinch! Shoot him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.16,0:15:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.91,0:15:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.04,0:15:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Put your hands up and kneel down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.29,0:15:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.08,0:15:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.96,0:16:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.88,0:16:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.13,0:16:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.30,0:16:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-Mika!\N-Mika...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.13,0:16:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, it hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.76,0:16:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty good, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.77,0:16:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Look what you did, you ruined\Nmy pretty face...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.02,0:16:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave your face full of holes too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.27,0:16:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Be grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.24,0:16:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... F-freeze...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.79,0:16:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Can't you see the gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sto-...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.68,0:16:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Bullshit...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.64,0:17:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen someone who'd\Nboard a pirate ship alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.31,0:17:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Never in my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.23,0:17:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Who on earth are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.78,0:17:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a draker.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.70,0:17:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Owww...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.16,0:17:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.66,0:17:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have meat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.54,0:17:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Meat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.79,0:17:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.85,0:17:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.35,0:17:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You eat surprisingly well, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.52,0:17:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you as much as you want,\Nbut get out of here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.64,0:17:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this bundle?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.60,0:17:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We happened to get some\Ngood dragon meat...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.08,0:17:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.29,0:17:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,"Lean dragon meat pastrami, pirate-style"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.70,0:18:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're making the spices work really well!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.50,0:18:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The fragance is great too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.25,0:18:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This smoked meat looks really good...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.04,0:18:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of dish is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.54,0:18:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa... Pastrami!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.55,0:18:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our family's secret recipe\Nthat uses a special spice blend!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.55,0:18:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.18,0:18:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And our special spice blend is
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,clove, cinnamon, and nutmeg
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.35,0:18:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,all mixed together, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.81,0:18:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a high-class item,\Nalso called allspice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Savour it thoroughly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.70,0:18:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.07,0:18:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.21,0:18:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit, it jammed at the worst moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.63,0:18:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I lowered my guard because I was hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.93,0:18:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You were hiding there, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.14,0:19:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who shot at Takita, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Y... Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.75,0:19:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Mika-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.46,0:19:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.71,0:19:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.63,0:19:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They said they'd share food with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.17,0:19:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.13,0:19:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.39,0:19:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He suppressed it all by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.55,0:19:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He's messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.56,0:19:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just how he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.14,0:19:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know who are\Nthe pirates anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.82,0:19:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.87,0:20:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.37,0:20:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! A dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.25,0:20:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Above the clouds! It's inside the sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.25,0:20:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohh! It looks pretty voluminous too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.09,0:20:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll leave as soon as Mika's up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.18,0:20:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro, don't lose sight of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.64,0:20:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, to your positions!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.52,0:20:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,For the love of god, please catch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.35,0:20:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If you let it go, I won't be able\Nto pay your salaries!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.24,0:20:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They were... amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.74,0:20:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... they're something else...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.66,0:20:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Drakers... huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.52,0:21:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He looks so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.95,0:21:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,♪〜
